title: For diversified industrial uses in accordance with the industrial location policy, with office space
clause_text: For diversified industrial uses in accordance with the industrial location policy, with office space only ancillary to and required for such uses, subject to and observance of all other Regulations; For commercial purposes, as permitted under these Regulations; Open lands and balance FSI shall be used as in the Table below:-
